metadata.description:
888 started as an experiment where I was chopping up a song that I had written 2 years ago called "goodbye." I wanted to bring it back to life with a bit more energy, but still not take away from the core meaning of the original idea. There have been a million different versions of this idea, and I couldn't be more proud of the final. This track is a part of my EP "TASTE" that is releasing on all platforms 10.21.22

we gon make it thru it
this won't last forever
I promise it gets better
